"[DIALOG_START][Mega]\n"
"Up next, I'll explain about\n"
"Countering and Bonus Cards.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"If you land a card attack\n"
"on an enemy just as they're\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"about to attack, that's a\n"
"Counter.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"That'll catch them off-guard,\n"
"paralyzing them for a time.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"You'll also receive a Bonus\n"
"Card for doing so.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Usually, you can only use\n"
"cards you select on the\n"
"Custom Screen. But if you\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"land a Counter, then you'll\n"
"be rewarded a Bonus Card.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Bonus Cards are chosen\n"
"from your Card Folder\n"
"at random.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Even so, they're great\n"
"because you don't have to\n"
"wait for the Custom Gauge\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"to fill up before going buck\n"
"wild on the enemy!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"But, you can't get another\n"
"Bonus Card if you pull off a\n"
"Counter with a Bonus Card.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Countering is pretty hard to\n"
"pull off, so you should work\n"
"on your timing for a bit.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Try to use a Bonus Card to\n"
"delete all the enemies in\n"
"one turn!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Megaman]\n"
"I want to say \"understood\",\n"
"but it's been a while\n"
"since I last battled...\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"It might take a little bit for\n"
"it all to come back to me.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Mega]\n"
"Why does it feel like I've\n"
"heard that before...?\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Oh well! Just this once I'll\n"
"help you with the timing, but\n"
"just this once, you hear!?\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"I can't focus on the battle\n"
"if I'm trying to tell you what\n"
"to do all the time!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Megaman]\n"
"Thanks, Mega!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Mega]\n"
"Yeah, yeah, yeah.\n"
"So, this is how I'll help you\n"
"with the Counter timing...\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"I'll stick an arrow on top of\n"
"the head of enemies that\n"
"can be Countered.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"You'll achieve a Counter if\n"
"you hit the enemy while the\n"
"arrow is still over its head.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"There are Battle Cards that\n"
"hit the enemy right away...\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"But there are also ones\n"
"that take more time to hit\n"
"enemies.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"So, do your best to make\n"
"Battle Cards hit the enemy\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"while the arrow is still over\n"
"its head.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Megaman]\n"
"Got it!\n"
"I'm ready to try it out now!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"{ec00}{1}"
msgstr ""
"{ec00}{0}\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Mega]\n"
"Vale,ahora toca el\n"
"Contraataque y las\n"
"cartas de bonificación.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"En un Contraataque,\n"
"golpeas a un enemigo con\n"
"una carta en el mismo\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"momento en que está a\n"
"punto de atacarte.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Eso les pillará por\n"
"sorpresa, y estarán\n"
"un rato paralizados.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Además, recibirás una\n"
"carta de bonificación.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Normalmente, solo puedes\n"
"usar cartas que tengas\n"
"en la pantalla de cartas.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Pero si haces un\n"
"contraataque, recibirás\n"
"una carta de bonificación.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Son cartas elegidas de\n"
"forma aleatoria de\n"
"tu carpeta.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"¡Pero son la bomba, así\n"
"no tienes que esperar a\n"
"que se llene la Carga\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"de cartas para acabar\n"
"cuanto antes con el\n"
"enemigo!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Un contraataque con una\n"
"carta de bonificación no\n"
"te dará otra carta.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Los contraataques son\n"
"difíciles, fíjate bien\n"
"en los tiempos.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"¡Usa una carta de\n"
"bonificación para acabar\n"
"con todos en un turno!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Megaman]\n"
"Me gustaría decir «entendido»,\n"
"pero hace mucho que\n"
"no combato...\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Puede que tarde un poco\n"
"en pillarle el truco.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Mega]\n"
"Acabo de tener un deja vu...\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"¡En fin! ¡Solo por esta\n"
"vez te ayudaré a hacerlo\n"
"en el momento justo!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"¡Si tengo que decirte todo\n"
"el rato qué hacer, no puedo\n"
"centrarme en el combate!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Megaman]\n"
"¡Gracias, Mega!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Mega]\n"
"Sí, sí, sí.\n"
"A ver, atento a cómo te\n"
"voy a ayudar a contraatacar.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Voy a mostrar una flecha\n"
"sobre la cabeza del\n"
"enemigo a contraatacar.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Si atacas al enemigo cuando\n"
"tenga la flecha, lanzarás\n"
"un contraataque.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Hay cartas de combate que\n"
"golpean al enemigo al\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"instante, pero otras\n"
"necesitan más tiempo.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"Así que calcula el tiempo\n"
"para golpear al enemigo\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"cuando el enemigo tenga\n"
"la flecha en la cabeza.\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"\n"
"[DIALOG_START][Megaman]\n"
"¡Entendido! ¡Voy a\n"
"intentarlo ahora mismo!\n"
"[NEW_DIALOG]\n"
"{ec00}{1}"

